en: After all, the first feed station held for two years before the inner metal ring for the lid fitting was removed from the wire mesh. But when ordering a replacement, the lid is very bad at the time of delivery, so that I will now finally decide for another feeding station. Perhaps the real problem lies in the fact that the wire mesh is quite flexible, so that the cylinder deforms in the longitudinal direction.

en: I bought the adapter to connect it to my Thunderbolt display. I work with a 15" MacBook Pro 2019. The recessions didn't stop me. However, the adapter does not charge reliably. it does not manage to maintain the battery level with stronger use of the notebook. In addition, my Mac has repeatedly made the tone of the "full charge state". Although it was actually full. This is unfortunately nothing I want to do to my battery and therefore goes back.

Geschmacklich ist der Ristretto ein guter Espresso. Bedingt durch die vollkommen sinnlose Verpackung jedoch nur 2 Sterne. Geschmacklich wären es 4*.
en: In the search for alternative Nespresso capsules we have found here for the first time. In particular, the fact that the capsules are compostable and thus not working with aluminium as with other manufacturers was a purchasing argument. When unpacking then the disillusionment: each compostable capsule is welded again individually in plastic. The more positive environmental balance has thus been undone. The Ristretto is a good espresso. Due to the completely meaningless packaging, however, only 2 stars. The taste would be 4*.

The impression of the processing quality is very good. For travellers who value ultra-light luggage, it may be a little too heavy, but I prefer to buy a few grams of weight more, for which I have comfort, even on the go.
